## Downstream Analysis (optional)

### Step 10: Analyze test results

```
mcp_perfanalysis_analyze_test_results(test_run_id="<test_run_id>")
```

The PerfAnalysis MCP will automatically find `test-results.csv` in the `jmeter/` folder
if it does not exist in `blazemeter/` (fallback pattern documented in `docs/artifacts_guide.md`).

### Step 11: View in Streamlit UI

The KPI Dashboard will pick up the test run from the artifacts folder and display results.
The Streamlit UI uses the same fallback pattern.

